description: Retention of Campion House and Tigar Hall, demolition of annex buildings and outbuildings other than Tigar Hall, and redevelopment of the site including - Conversion of Campion House and erection of 13 new buildings to create 154 units (13 one-bedroom units, 96 two-bedroom units, 19 three-bedroom units (including 16 maisonettes) and 27 four-bedroom units (including 22 terraced houses and two semi-detached houses)); and - Conversion of Tigar Hall to provide a community facility and also to house an IT suite, exhibition space and site management office; and with associated parking, access and landscaping to site.
